definitions.definition: ( historical ) Someone freed from slavery in Ancient Rome ; a freedman .

main_definition: ( historical ) Someone freed from slavery in Ancient Rome ; a freedman .

definitions.definition: One who is freethinking in religious matters.
Someone (especially a man) who takes no notice of moral laws, especially those involving sexual propriety ; someone loose in morals; a pleasure - seeker .
